            <title><![CDATA[Gamers May Spend More Time Watching Games Than Playing Them]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/gamers-may-spend-more-time-watching-games-than-playing-them/1100-6528205/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/gamers-may-spend-more-time-watching-games-than-playing-them.1051083/</guid>
